---
interface Props {
  phone: string;
}

const { phone } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="mb-16">
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Comprehensive Boiler Services in Berks County</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
      Boilers are essential for keeping homes and businesses warm during Pennsylvania's colder months. Our boiler services in Berks County PA include everything from repairs and installations to routine maintenance, ensuring your system operates efficiently and reliably. Whether you need boiler repair in Berks County or are considering a new installation, our certified technicians are here to help.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
      From residential boiler services in Berks County to commercial boiler solutions, we handle projects of all sizes with professionalism and care.
    </p>
    
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <a href={`tel:${phone}`} class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-primary hover:bg-secondary">
